patterns-sap-minimal_sap 16.0-160000.2.2

bpftool 7.5.0-160000.2.2
libatomic1 15.1.1+git9973-160000.2.2
libltdl7 2.4.7-160000.2.2
polkit-default-privs 1550+20250604.71bfb94-160000.2.2
selinux-policy-sapenablement 1-160000.2.2
